Executive Profile
Marianne Boyd Johnson  Vice Chairman of the Board, Chief Diversity Officer and Executive Vice President, Boyd Gaming CorporationAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 4 Board Members in 4 different organizations across 4 different industries.See Board Relationships59--
Background

		Ms. Marianne Boyd Johnson has been a Vice President and Manager at Marina District Development Company LLC since April 01, 2005. Ms. Johnson has been an Executive Vice President of Boyd Gaming Corporation since January 2008 and also serves as its Chief Diversity Officer. Ms. Johnson served as a Vice President at Marina District Finance Company, Inc. from April 2005 to May 2010. She served as a Senior Vice President of Boyd Gaming Corp. since December 2001 until December ... 2007, Vice President from September 1997 to December 2001 and an Assistant Secretary since September 1989. From 1976 to September 1990, she held a variety of full and part-time positions with Boyd Gaming Corp., including participation in its Management Training Program and California Hotel and Casino. Ms. Johnson has been the Vice Chairman of Boyd Gaming Corporation since February 2001 and Director since September 1990. She has been a Director of Western Alliance Bancorporation since 1995 and Marina District Finance Company, Inc. since April 2005. She has been a Director of Western Alliance Bank at Western Alliance Bancorporation since March 2017. She served as a Director at BankWest of Nevada., a subsidiary of Western Alliance since 1994. Ms. Johnson served as a Director of Nevada Community Bank until 1993.Read Full Background




